#. Max bytes: 38
msgctxt "Offset_0x3CE4_Len_38"
msgid "Welcome!\nWhat can we do for you today?"
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 41
msgctxt "Offset_0x3DD4_Len_41"
msgid "I heard you offer personal training here."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 61
msgctxt "Offset_0x3ED4_Len_61"
msgid "You must be a new customer.\nAllow me to explain our services."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 82
msgctxt "Offset_0x3FF4_Len_82"
msgid "If you'd like to take advantage of our\nsports gym, you'll have to become a member."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 25
msgctxt "Offset_0x4134_Len_25"
msgid "Really? How do I do that?"
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 97
msgctxt "Offset_0x4224_Len_97"
msgid "Well, after listening to us explain the program,\nyou'll have to undergo a trial training session."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 79
msgctxt "Offset_0x4394_Len_79"
msgid "We'll design a personalized training regiment\njust for you based on that trial."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 79
msgctxt "Offset_0x44B4_Len_79"
msgid "Of course, you'll be able to approve \nthe contents before we finalize the plan."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 69
msgctxt "Offset_0x45E4_Len_69"
msgid "That could be interesting. All right,\ncan you tell me about your gym?"
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 79
msgctxt "Offset_0x4714_Len_79"
msgid "Just a moment. I'll bring the manager over.\nPlease take a seat in the meantime."
msgstr ""

#. Max bytes: 10
msgctxt "Offset_0x4834_Len_10"
msgid "All right."
msgstr ""

